ğŸŸª Module 12: File Sharing & Remote Access

SSH

ssh user@ip
scp file.txt user@ip:/tmp/


NFS

yum install nfs-utils -y
echo "/data *(rw,sync)" >> /etc/exports
exportfs -r
mount -t nfs server:/data /mnt

ğŸŸ¥ Module 13: Backup & Restore

Backup

